  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 27-7-22.48, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO REVISE THE DEFINITION OF \"ELIGIBLE CHARITABLE ORGANIZATION,\" FOR PURPOSES OF AN INDIVIDUAL AND BUSINESS INCOME TAX CREDIT, TO INCLUDE A 501(C)(3) ORGANIZATION THAT RAISES FUNDS FOR QUALIFIED TUITION PROGRAMS UNDER SECTION 529 OF THE INTERNAL REVENUE CODE FOR THE CHILDREN OF EMPLOYEES OF A MISSISSIPPI COUNTY SHERIFF'S DEPARTMENT OR MUNICIPAL POLICE DEPARTMENT; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
